  <!-- Call to Action Section -->
  <section id="cta" class="cta section">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="row" data-aos="zoom-in">
        <div class="col-lg-9 text-center text-lg-start">
          <h3>Ready to Start Your International Education Journey?</h3>
          <p>Get personalized guidance from our expert counselors to find the perfect study abroad program for you.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="col-lg-3 cta-btn-container text-center">
          <a class="cta-btn align-middle" href="/contact" data-bs-toggle="modal" data-bs-target="/contact">Book a Free Consultation</a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section><!-- End Call to Action Section -->

  <!-- FAQ Section -->
  <section id="faq" class="faq section">
    <div class="container">
      <h2 class="section-title">Frequently Asked Questions</h2>
      <div class="row">
        <div class="col-lg-6">
          <!-- FAQ List 1-->
          <div class="accordion accordion-flush" id="faqlist1">
            <div class="accordion-item">
              <h3 class="accordion-header">
                <button class="accordion-button collapsed" type="button" data-bs-toggle="collapse" data-bs-target="#faq-content-1">
                  How do I choose the right study abroad program?
                </button>
              </h3>
              <div id="faq-content-1" class="accordion-collapse collapse" data-bs-parent="#faqlist1">
                <div class="accordion-body">
                  Choosing the right program depends on various factors such as your academic interests, career goals, budget, and preferred location. Our expert counselors can help you evaluate these factors and find the best fit for you.
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>

            <div class="accordion-item">
              <h3 class="accordion-header">
                <button class="accordion-button collapsed" type="button" data-bs-toggle="collapse" data-bs-target="#faq-content-2">
                  What are the language requirements for studying abroad?
                </button>
              </h3>
              <div id="faq-content-2" class="accordion-collapse collapse" data-bs-parent="#faqlist1">
                <div class="accordion-body">
                  Language requirements vary by country and institution. Many English-speaking countries require proof of English proficiency through tests like IELTS or TOEFL. Some programs may require knowledge of the local language. We can guide you on specific requirements for your chosen program.
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>

            <div class="accordion-item">
              <h3 class="accordion-header">
                <button class="accordion-button collapsed" type="button" data-bs-toggle="collapse" data-bs-target="#faq-content-3">
                  How much does it cost to study abroad?
                </button>
              </h3>
              <div id="faq-content-3" class="accordion-collapse collapse" data-bs-parent="#faqlist1">
                <div class="accordion-body">
                  Costs vary widely depending on the country, institution, and program. They typically include tuition fees, living expenses, health insurance, and travel costs. We can provide detailed cost breakdowns for different programs and help you explore financing options and scholarships.
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="col-lg-6">
          <!-- FAQ List 2-->
          <div class="accordion accordion-flush" id="faqlist2">
            <div class="accordion-item">
              <h3 class="accordion-header">
                <button class="accordion-button collapsed" type="button" data-bs-toggle="collapse" data-bs-target="#faq2-content-1">
                  Can I work while studying abroad?
                </button>
              </h3>
              <div id="faq2-content-1" class="accordion-collapse collapse" data-bs-parent="#faqlist2">
                <div class="accordion-body">
                  Work regulations for international students vary by country. Many countries allow students to work part-time during their studies and full-time during breaks. We can provide specific information on work rights for your chosen destination.
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>

            <div class="accordion-item">
              <h3 class="accordion-header">
                <button class="accordion-button collapsed" type="button" data-bs-toggle="collapse" data-bs-target="#faq2-content-2">
                  How do I apply for a student visa?
                </button>
              </h3>
              <div id="faq2-content-2" class="accordion-collapse collapse" data-bs-parent="#faqlist2">
                <div class="accordion-body">
                  The visa application process differs for each country. Generally, you'll need an acceptance letter from your chosen institution, proof of funds, and other supporting documents. Our team can guide you through the entire visa application process for your specific destination.
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>

            <div class="accordion-item">
              <h3 class="accordion-header">
                <button class="accordion-button collapsed" type="button" data-bs-toggle="collapse" data-bs-target="#faq2-content-3">
                  What support services are available for international students?
                </button>
              </h3>
              <div id="faq2-content-3" class="accordion-collapse collapse" data-bs-parent="#faqlist2">
                <div class="accordion-body">
                  Most universities offer comprehensive support services for international students, including orientation programs, academic advising, career services, health services, and cultural integration support. We can provide details on the specific services available at your chosen institution.
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section><!-- End FAQ Section -->


    </section><!-- /Courses Section -->

  </main>
